example.code:
1/  Today I launched {product}.

    {one-line value prop, e.g. "Turn your customer interviews
    into a positioning statement in 5 minutes."}

    Thread on what, why, and how to try it: ↓

2/  [demo.gif — 8s gif of the core flow]

    {3-7 word caption}

3/  The problem:

    {1-2 line description of the pain — real, not abstract.
    Include a moment of recognition for the target user.}

4/  How {product} solves it:

    {1-2 line summary of the mechanism. Concrete verbs:
    "loads transcripts → tags forces → emits statement".}

5/  Pricing:
    - {Free / trial tier}
    - {Paid tier 1}
    - {Paid tier 2}

    {one-line rationale, e.g. "lifetime deal for first 100 users"}

6/  Try it today: {landing_url}

    {one-line CTA + optional "DM me for feedback"}

7/  Early users say:

    "{verbatim user quote with name + role}"
    {OR metric: "$X MRR in N days"}

    [screenshot.png — dashboard or testimonial card]
